data.description: Contract Pending Welcome to your Mid Century Modern oasis. This meticulously cared for home has only had two owners. It's full of floor to ceiling windows, 4 gorgeous skylights throughout provide all natural lighting. There’s endless purposeful storage, a huge heated garage with a cedar closet, fire place, sprinkler system, wired for built-in indoor/outdoor speaker system. The outdoor space is very private with multiple mature trees, stunning gardens sitting on almost half an acre. The entire house was re-carpeted and repainted, newer roof and new gutters and downspouts, radon mitigation system and so much more to love!
